
1. Open Directory > Point to vagrant root folder  
2. Settings > Python Interpreters (second last icon in menu bar, besides help (?))  
- Add remore python interpreter, incase it does not exist. (Click on the + icon)  
Host: 127.0.0.1
Port: 2222
Username: vagrant
Auth type: Password
Password: vagrant (save password)
Test conntection - (test if connection is successful, start vm if required)  
Python interpreter Path: /vagrant/bin/python  
Apply - OK
3. Settings > Project Structure
Select src - click on Sources menu above
Select src/apps - click on Sources menu above
Source folders in left get updated to src and src/apps  
Apply - Ok  





